  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed rear dormer, by reason of its scale, size and detailed design, would result in an incompatible form of development, which would adversely affect the character and appearance of the host building resulting in the loss of a characterful roof form and harm the character of the wider terrace within which it is located. As such, the proposal is considered contrary to the policies D4 (Delivering good design) of the London Plan (2021) and Policy LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) of Hackney’s Local Plan 2033 (2020) and the relevant sections of the Hackney’s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
